snippet.title: Just Dance 2014: E3 2013 Trailer [UK]
snippet.description:
The latest opus of Just Dance franchise will make you dance even more, featuring the hottest hits, exciting new features and the coolest moves letting you and your friends experience parties the way only Just Dance knows how!  

Just Dance 2014 is  the future of party gaming !

More Information on: http://www.justdancegame.com/
